title: Mayor Durkan on Keeping Politics Out of Reopening
itunes:title: Mayor Durkan on Keeping Politics Out of Reopening
description:
Seattle Mayor Jenny Durkan discusses why cities need to be "smart" with plans to reopen their economies. She says bipartisan cooperation is needed to get America back to work.

Hosts: Carol Massar and Jason Kelly. Producer: Doni Holloway.
